                <li><code>PreToolUse</code> exit <code>2</code> blocks the tool AND surfaces stderr to the agent. Only blocking hook.</li>
                <li>Sub-agent's own loop has its own <code>PreToolUse</code>/<code>PostToolUse</code> calls — they share <code>session_id</code>.</li>
