          <p class="card-sub" style="margin-top:10px">precedência &amp; ordem de load</p>
          <p class="mini">
            <b>Settings:</b> managed-policy → CLI flags → <code>settings.local.json</code> → <code>.claude/settings.json</code> → <code>~/.claude/settings.json</code>. First match wins per key.
          </p>
          <p class="mini" style="margin-top:4px">
            <b>CLAUDE.md walk:</b> managed-policy → <code>~/.claude/CLAUDE.md</code> → ancestors of cwd → <code>./CLAUDE.md</code> → <code>CLAUDE.local.md</code> → nested subdir <code>CLAUDE.md</code> (on-demand when files in those dirs are touched).
          </p>
          <p class="mini" style="margin-top:4px">
            <b>Managed policy</b> (admin-pushed, cannot be excluded): <code>/etc/claude-code/</code> Linux/WSL · <code>/Library/Application Support/ClaudeCode/</code> macOS · <code>C:\Program Files\ClaudeCode\</code> Windows. Holds <code>CLAUDE.md</code> + <code>managed-settings.json</code>.
          </p>
          <p class="mini" style="margin-top:8px">
            <b>Rule of thumb:</b> teammate cloning your repo should get it → <code>&lt;proj&gt;/.claude/</code> · only you should have it → <code>~/.claude/</code> · per-machine local → <code>settings.local.json</code> (gitignored).
          </p>
        </article>

